headline.main: Rescue Helicopter Crashes in Central Japan; At Least 3 Dead
headline.print_headline: Rescue Helicopter Crashes in Central Japan; At Least 3 Dead

lead_paragraph: The killing of the estranged half-brother of North Korea's leader who had been living in the Chinese territory of Macau may be top news around the world, but for some Macanese legislators at China's parliament it's more a case of Kim Jong Who?
